，愿意去改变。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I9v/2wa3Ox5s8EAMaCDY3NzEzMDk2IKbD64cGMAA4zwFAG3IJNDc0NDQ4MTY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"53 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-136210e0f43c1ec9e70ce987c0ec6540_1440w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1627345188.7468083","card_id":"Q_400192435","target":{"id":400192435,"title":"路飞对克比的评价很高，尾田也着力暗示克比的成功，为什么很多人仍然不看好克比？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/400192435","type":"question","created":1591604373,"answer_count":167,"follower_count":262,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[392,48237,161702,396543],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I9v/2wa3Ox5s8EAMaCDUxMjEwNDczIJXp9/YFMAU4hgJAHHIJNDAwMTkyNDM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"52 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1627345188.7470646","card_id":"Q_474700969","target":{"id":474700969,"title":"有了两部《白蛇》的成功基础，追光动画有可能做出「追光宇宙」吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/474700969","type":"question","created":1627132860,"answer_count":39,"follower_count":84,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[114774,230501,665396],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"两部《白蛇》都取得了不错的成绩，第一部堪称当年黑马，第二部上映一填票房已破一亿。从彩蛋出现的宝青坊主、杨戬线索看，新的作品也在计划中。那么按照目前的布局，追光有可能成功做出中国版漫威宇宙吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj4I9v/2wa3Ox5s8EAMaCDY3NzY5MzA0ILyn8IcGMAQ4VEAdcgk0NzQ3MDA5Njl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-68868eb69969f7a457362455dd3ce273_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_16273